## Context Compression Rules

### Player Data
- Player ID: First 6 chars only
- Username: Full name (already short)
- Chips: `Chips:1000` instead of `Chips: $1000`
- Seat: `Seat:1` instead of `Seat: 1`

### Game Data
- Table: `Table:25` instead of `Table: 25`
- Phase: `Phase:preflop` instead of `Phase: preflop`
- Pot: `Pot:200` instead of `Pot: $200`
- Bet: `bet:50` instead of `Bet: $50`

### Error Data
- Error: `Error:AlreadyTaken` instead of `Error: Seat already taken`
- Retry: `Retry:3/5` instead of `Retry attempt 3 of 5`
- Status: `Status:Failed` instead of `Status: Failed`

